Date: Sun, 29 Mar 2026 11:47:59 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 22/22] fix: make CI green by fixing path-help service and
 date-format test

- Revert path-help service to use newModel.attributes instead of store.modelFor
- Remove unnecessary store injection from path-help service
- Update date-format test to expect correct string lengths (23 without timezone, 32 with timezone)

Signed-off-by: Aditya <jaiswal.aditya.deelip@gmail.com>
---
 ui/app/services/path-help.js                     | 15 +++------------
 ui/tests/integration/helpers/date-format-test.js |  6 +++---
 2 files changed, 6 insertions(+), 15 deletions(-)

diff --git a/ui/app/services/path-help.js b/ui/app/services/path-help.js
index 68d1c8c..61a3eb4 100644
--- a/ui/app/services/path-help.js
+++ b/ui/app/services/path-help.js
@@ -9,7 +9,7 @@
   has less (or no) information about.
